t: "Then (on) the Resurrection Day He shames/scandalizes/disgraces them, and he says: \"Where (are) my partners those who you were making animosity/revolting/disobe ying in (because of) them?\" Those who were given the knowledge said: \"That the shame/scandal/disgrace, today , and the bad/evil/harm (is) on the disbelievers"